---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Code of Conduct - Cocoboko Studios">
    <Navigation />
    
    <main class="bg-slate-800 min-h-screen text-white py-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Cocoboko Community Code of Conduct</h1>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">☕ Cocoboko Community Code of Conduct</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                Welcome to the Cocoboko community — which includes our Discord server, the Cocoboko Café — a cozy space to chat, chill, and connect around games, creativity, and community. Before joining the conversation, please take a moment to read and respect these guidelines.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">🧠 Be Thoughtful. Be Kind.</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                We’re all human here. That means we bring different backgrounds, experiences, identities, and opinions — and that’s a good thing. Treat everyone with <strong>respect</strong>, even when you disagree. Listen more than you talk. Assume good intent. Kindness is not optional.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">🚫 Zero Tolerance for Harassment</h2>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300">
                <li>Racist, sexist, or ableist language</li>
                <li>Personal attacks or name-calling</li>
                <li>Unwanted DMs, especially for self-promotion</li>
                <li>Jokes that punch down or make others uncomfortable</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">If you cross the line, we’ll act — including bans without warning.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">💬 Keep It Clean & Constructive</h2>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300">
                <li>Use appropriate language</li>
                <li>Share content that’s safe for work</li>
                <li>Avoid spam, trolling, or derailment</li>
                <li>Respect content warnings and boundaries</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">🚧 No Politics, No Drama</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Our community isn’t the place for debating current events or engaging in flamewars. Keep discussion focused on games, creativity, and chill conversation.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">📣 Promote with Permission</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Sharing your work? Awesome — we love that! But please only post links or self-promotion in the <strong>designated spaces (like channels on our Discord)</strong> and with intention. No drive-by link drops.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">🛠️ Moderators Have Your Back</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Mods are here to help keep the space welcoming. If you see something concerning or feel uncomfortable, please DM a mod (via Discord) or use the report feature on platforms that support it. We’ll listen and act discreetly.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">✅ One Rule Above All</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                <strong>Respect the human on the other side of the screen.</strong><br />
                If you’re ever unsure, err on the side of empathy.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <p class="text-gray-300 italic">
                Thanks for being here. Grab a seat, pour your favorite drink, and let’s make something great together.
              </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
